Millennium%20at%20about%20%2414%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal%20who%20wasn't%20authorized%20to%20share%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Millennium%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pleased%20to%20announce%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20the%20sale%20of%20a%20minority%2C%20passive%20equity%20interest%20in%20Millennium's%20management%20company.%20This%20transaction%20is%20the%20latest%20step%20in%20our%20evolution%20and%20further%20positions%20Millennium%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20reads%20in%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Millennium's%20largest%20existing%20backers%20participated%20in%20the%20deal%2C%20according%20to%20the%20memo.%20It%20was%20executed%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Asset%20Management's%20Petershill%20unit%2C%20which%20makes%20minority%20investments%20in%20private-equity%20firms%2C%20hedge%20funds%2C%20and%20other%20alternative%20investment%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennium%20charges%20fees%20and%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20fund's%20performance%20to%20manage%20capital.%20Englander%20and%20other%20equity%20holders%20get%20a%20slice%20of%20that%20income%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennium%2C%20founded%20in%201989%20by%20Englander%2C%20has%20grown%20into%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20hedge%20funds%20globally%2C%20with%20over%206%2C400%20employees%20and%20330%20investment%20teams%20managing%20%2479%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund's%20long-running%20success%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20averaged%20a%20return%20of%20about%2014%25%20annually%20since%20inception%20and%20has%20only%20lost%20money%20once%20in%2035%20years%20%E2%80%94%20has%20fueled%20that%20growth%20and%20enabled%20it%20to%20secure%20a%20more%20stable%20capital%20base%20than%20most%20hedge%20funds%2C%20locking%20up%20investor%20cash%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20significant%20valuation%2C%20especially%20when%20compared%20to%20others%20