3E%3Cp%3EIn%20suburbia%2C%20if%20we%20needed%20something%20for%20a%20recipe%2C%20we%20would%20stop%20at%20the%20store%20and%20easily%20find%20it.%20Now%2C%20we%20order%20oyster%20sauce%20from%20Amazon%20and%20stock%20up%20on%20perishables%20midweek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20area%20isn't%20exactly%20a%20food%20desert%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20plan%20meals%20and%20eat%20healthily%20when%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20will%20be%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229192fce3-a524-4df6-a9d8-ad820b0c2348%5C%22%3ELimited%20healthcare%20options%20mean%20long%20wait%20times%20and%20lengthy%20drives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Becki%20Rupp%20smiling%20with%20mountains%20in%20distance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e812cf1c1f80efbec54db8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20years%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20dreamed%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20the%20Rockies.%3Cp%3EBecki%20Rupp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20considered%20the%20healthcare%20situation%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-small-town-from-big-city-surprising-benefits-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20a%20more%20remote%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20regional%20medical%20center%20in%20town%20includes%20hospital%20services%20and%20several%20specialists%2C%20so%20we%20figured%20we'd%20be%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20didn't%20realize%20is%20that%20the%20ratio%20of%20medical%20providers%20to%20the%20population%20can%20sometimes%20result%20in%20long%20waiting%20times%20for%20appointments%20and%20limited%20choices%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20certain%20advanced%20care%2C%20many%20locals%20drive%20to%20Denver%20%E2%80%94%20about%20a%20five-hour%20round%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20life-threatening%20emergencies%2C%20patients%20are%20sometimes%20flown%20by%20helicopter%20to%20Colorado%20Springs%20or%20Denver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20grateful%20for%20the%20care%20we%20can%20and%20do%20get%20locally%3B%20some%20rural%20communities%20don't%20even%20have%20a%20doctor%20nearby.%20As%20we%20age%2C%20though%2C%20the%20limits%20on%20local%20healthcare%20weigh%20more%20heavily%20on%20our%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ee6ae81-daa3-4f77-a2dd-fcbfb1d12a9b%5C%22%3EWe're%20worried%20about%20how%20easily%20we%20can%20lose%20service%20and%20access%20to%20emergency%20resources%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20on%20mountain%20bike%20in%20mountains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e813191c1f80efbec54dca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESometimes%20we%20lose%20service%20in%20our%20more%20remote%20area.%3Cp%3EBecki%20Rupp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobal-it-outage-y2k-24-years-later-crowdstrike-cyber-expert-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWidespread%20service%20outages%3C%2Fa%3E%20weren't%20something%20we%20really%20worried%20about%20or%20broadly%20experienced%20until%20we%20moved%20to%20a%20more%20rural%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20county%20has%20a%20very%20limited%20number%20of%20telecommunications%20fiber-optic%20lines%2C%20and%20we%20can%20lose%20cellphone%20and%20internet%20service%20if%20one%20gets%20cut%20during%20construction%20or%20a%20wildfire%20destroys%20the%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20without%20major%20issues%2C%20we%20still%20find%20ourselves%20suddenly%20losing%20connectivity%20for%20several%20hours%20here%20and%20there.%20A%20few%20summers%20ago%2C%20service%20was%20disrupted%20across%20nearly%20our%20entire%20county.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGas%20pumps%2C%20stores%2C%20and%20restaurants%20were%20unable%20to%20process%20credit-card%20transactions.%20Local%20ATMs%20weren't%20wo